    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the SEED encryption algorithm, which has been adopted by most of the security systems in the Republic of Korea. Included are a description of the encryption and the key scheduling algorithm (Section 2), the S-boxes (Appendix A), and a set of test vectors (Appendix B).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document obsoletes RFC 4009. This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
